fields.description: The ARM resource id in the form of /subscriptions/{SubscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{ResourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Compute/sshPublicKeys/{SshPublicKeyName}
fields.name: Id

fields.description: Private key portion of the key pair used to authenticate to a virtual machine through ssh. The private key is returned in RFC3447 format and should be treated as a secret.
fields.name: PrivateKey

fields.description: Public key portion of the key pair used to authenticate to a virtual machine through ssh. The public key is in ssh-rsa format.
fields.name: PublicKey
